is almost ready.
Bring her

879
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:16,639
a bowl later.

880
00:39:16,960 --> 00:39:17,440
No.
You go.

881
00:39:18,760 --> 00:39:19,920
Why?

882
00:39:20,440 --> 00:39:21,400
She probably can't face me

883
00:39:22,079 --> 00:39:22,960
for the next few days.

884
00:39:25,280 --> 00:39:26,159
Can't face you?

885
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:39,440
Where's Ye?

886
00:39:40,320 --> 00:39:40,800
She left.

887
00:39:41,519 --> 00:39:42,400
What about the popsicle?
You've worked hard.

888
00:39:43,519 --> 00:39:44,280
You can have two.

889
00:39:44,840 --> 00:39:45,280
All right.

890
00:39:46,360 --> 00:39:47,559
What did you two do

891
00:39:47,960 --> 00:39:48,559
last night?

892
00:39:48,880 --> 00:39:49,599
None of your business.

893
00:40:05,880 --> 00:40:06,440
Here you go.

894
00:40:07,039 --> 00:40:08,159
Everything you asked for.

895
00:40:08,440 --> 00:40:10,320
That'll be 220 yuan.

896
00:40:11,639 --> 00:40:12,960
Could you give me a discount

897
00:40:13,639 --> 00:40:15,280
This is already the lowest.

898
00:40:16,880 --> 00:40:18,079
That young man,

899
00:40:18,719 --> 00:40:19,960
Xing Wu,

900
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:21,159
you know him?

901
00:40:21,400 --> 00:40:22,400
He's my cousin.

902
00:40:22,599 --> 00:40:23,960
Your cousin?

903
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:27,119
Alright then, I'll give you 20% off.

904
00:40:28,079 --> 00:40:29,559
176 yuan.

905
00:40:29,920 --> 00:40:30,639
Really?

906
00:40:31,480 --> 00:40:33,199
Then I owe him one.

907
00:40:34,039 --> 00:40:34,960
Not really.

908
00:40:35,159 --> 00:40:37,199
He's always fixing things for me,

909
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:39,079
so giving you a discount

910
00:40:39,199 --> 00:40:39,960
is the least I can do.

911
00:40:40,719 --> 00:40:41,920
Whenever

912
00:40:42,199 --> 00:40:43,199
anything breaks in town,

913
00:40:43,320 --> 00:40:44,199
people go to him.

914
00:40:44,440 --> 00:40:45,360
Everyone knows him.

915
00:40:46,599 --> 00:40:47,480
QR code's right there.
Got it.

916
00:41:05,719 --> 00:41:07,119
[Thanks to you, my celebrity cousin,]

917
00:41:07,280 --> 00:41:08,519
[the print shop owner gave me 20% off.]

918
00:41:36,320 --> 00:41:37,119
Did Ye make this?

919
00:41:40,159 --> 00:41:40,760
Wu,

920
00:41:41,079 --> 00:41:42,480
that neck pillow

921
00:41:42,679 --> 00:41:43,599
is hers too, right?

922
00:41:49,280 --> 00:41:50,440
Xuan Island's gonna be a hit.

923
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:52,280
With poster this nice,

924
00:41:52,719 --> 00:41:54,119
business has to pick up.

925
00:41:59,119 --> 00:41:59,639
Oh,

926
00:42:00,320 --> 00:42:01,440
I have some good news.

927
00:42:02,719 --> 00:42:03,320
What is it?

928
00:42:03,880 --> 00:42:04,800
Han's business trip is over.

929
00:42:05,039 --> 00:42:05,800
She's coming back today.

930
00:42:06,719 --> 00:42:07,280
Really?

931
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:08,679
She didn't tell me.

932
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:10,760
Maybe

933
00:42:10,880 --> 00:42:12,079
she wanted to give you a surprise.

934
00:42:15,960 --> 00:42:17,199
Did I spoil it?

935
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:19,400
Just pretend you didn't know.

936
00:42:20,400 --> 00:42:20,800
Okay.

937
00:43:02,480 --> 00:43:04,440
Hop in. I'll give you a ride.

938
00:43:05,840 --> 00:43:06,559
Where are you going?
Zhazhating.

939
00:43:08,679 --> 00:43:09,440
Come on, get in.

940
00:43:09,440 --> 00:43:10,679
Don't worry, I'm not a bad guy.

941
00:43:10,840 --> 00:43:11,719
I'm not charging you either.

942
00:43:15,639 --> 00:43:16,159
Okay.

943
00:43:22,079 --> 00:43:23,360
Too much stuff in the back.

944
00:43:23,480 --> 00:43:24,320
You have to sit up front.

945
00:43:24,800 --> 00:43:25,679
Okay. Thanks.

946
00:43:26,239 --> 00:43:27,639
Here's a tissue. Dry your hair.

947
00:43:30,360 --> 00:43:31,039
Hainan?

948
00:43:32,000 --> 00:43:32,440
Yeah.

949
00:43:32,559 --> 00:43:33,960
I just got back from a business trip there.
